      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Mr Whinnyham closes his eyes and tries to remember the missing clothes...\nOne
    missing item is bright red and hides a detective\u2019s tired eyes from curious
    strangers.\r\nOne missing item  is blue and keeps your head dry when the rain
    starts to fall.\r\nOne missing item is dark black, heavy and warm \u2014 perfect
    for cold nights and secret investigations.\r\nCan you identify the missing clothes?"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
